Class CFGProductionRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • syntaxParseTools.CFGProductionRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<CFGProductionRule>, GrammarRule<CFGProductionRule>

    public class CFGProductionRule
extends java.lang.Object
implements GrammarRule<CFGProductionRule>
    CFG production rules are of the form:
    NODE1 :- NODE2, ..., NODEn
    where NODE1 is the only node on the left hand side of the production and there are n nodes on the right hand side of the production.
    In this program, n is >= 1, but has no upper constraint.
    Author:
    glpayson
